<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Raport z badania słuchu — SprawdźSłuch</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #0E7490;
            --primary-dark: #155E75;
            --primary-light: #CFFAFE;
            --accent: #16A34A;
            --accent-dark: #15803D;

            --text: #1F2937;
            --text-soft: #4B5563;
            --text-muted: #6B7280;
            --line: #E5E7EB;
            --bg: #F8F9FA;

            --normal: #1F7F1F;
            --mild: #8A6100;
            --moderate: #B4470F;
            --severe: #9F2417;
            --profound: #5B3A78;
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        html { -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; print-color-adjust: exact; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            color: var(--text);
            background: #fff;
            font-size: 13px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .sheet { padding: 0 14mm; }

        /* ---------- Letterhead ---------- */
        .letterhead {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding-bottom: 9px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid transparent;
            border-image: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary) 55%, var(--accent) 100%) 1;
        }
        .brand .logo {
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
            color: var(--primary);
        }
        .brand .logo .g { color: var(--accent); }
        .brand .tagline {
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }
        .doc-meta { text-align: right; }
        .doc-meta .doc-kind {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--primary);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.8px;
        }
        .doc-meta .doc-row {
            font-size: 10.5px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-top: 3px;
        }
        .doc-meta .doc-row b { color: var(--text); font-weight: 700; }

        /* ---------- Sections ---------- */
        .section { margin-top: 18px; break-inside: avoid; }
        .section-head {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .section-head .ico {
            width: 26px; height: 26px;
            flex: 0 0 26px;
            border-radius: 7px;
            background: var(--primary-light);
            color: var(--primary);
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
        }
        .section-head .ico svg { width: 15px; height: 15px; }
        .section-title {
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--text);
            letter-spacing: -0.2px;
        }

        .card {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 18px 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.04);
            break-inside: avoid;
        }

        /* ---------- Result summary hero ---------- */
        .summary {
            margin-top: 14px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 16px 24px 18px;
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-left: 6px solid var(--primary);
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #EFF9FB 0%, #fff 100%);
            break-inside: avoid;
        }
        .summary.level-normal   { border-left-color: var(--normal);   background: linear-gradient(180deg, #F1FBF4 0%, #fff 70%); }
        .summary.level-mild     { border-left-color: var(--mild);     background: linear-gradient(180deg, #FCF6E9 0%, #fff 70%); }
        .summary.level-moderate { border-left-color: var(--moderate); background: linear-gradient(180deg, #FCEFE6 0%, #fff 70%); }
        .summary.level-severe   { border-left-color: var(--severe);   background: linear-gradient(180deg, #FBEAE6 0%, #fff 70%); }
        .summary.level-profound { border-left-color: var(--profound); background: linear-gradient(180deg, #F3ECF6 0%, #fff 70%); }

        .summary-label {
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }
        .summary-status {
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
            margin: 4px 0 6px;
        }
        .level-normal   .summary-status { color: var(--normal); }
        .level-mild     .summary-status { color: var(--mild); }
        .level-moderate .summary-status { color: var(--moderate); }
        .level-severe   .summary-status { color: var(--severe); }
        .level-profound .summary-status { color: var(--profound); }

        .summary-meaning {
            font-size: 12.5px;
            color: var(--text-soft);
            max-width: 95%;
        }

        /* severity meter */
        .meter-wrap { margin-top: 12px; }
        .meter-scalelabels {
            display: flex; justify-content: space-between;
            font-size: 9px; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 4px; padding: 0 1px;
        }
        .meter {
            position: relative;
            height: 12px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg,
                var(--normal) 0%, var(--normal) 20%,
                #C99700 20%, #C99700 40%,
                var(--moderate) 40%, var(--moderate) 70%,
                #C0392B 70%, #C0392B 100%);
        }
        .meter-marker {
            position: absolute;
            top: -5px;
            width: 4px; height: 22px;
            background: #0F172A;
            border-radius: 2px;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px #fff;
        }
        .meter-caption {
            font-size: 10.5px; color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-top: 8px; font-weight: 600;
        }
        .meter-caption b { color: var(--text); }

        /* stat chips */
        .stats { display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-top: 12px; }
        .stat {
            flex: 1;
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-radius: 11px;
            padding: 9px 14px;
        }
        .stat .k { font-size: 9.5px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-muted); }
        .stat .v { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary-dark); margin-top: 3px; }

        /* ---------- Info grid ---------- */
        .info-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .info-item {
            padding: 11px 14px;
            background: var(--bg);
            border-radius: 10px;
            border-left: 3px solid var(--primary);
        }
        .info-label { font-size: 9.5px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-muted); }
        .info-value { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); margin-top: 3px; }

        .receipt {
            margin-top: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            background: #F1FBF4;
            border: 1px solid #BDEBCB;
            border-radius: 11px;
            padding: 12px 16px;
        }
        .receipt .check {
            width: 30px; height: 30px; flex: 0 0 30px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--accent);
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
        }
        .receipt .check svg { width: 17px; height: 17px; color: #fff; }
        .receipt-title { font-size: 12.5px; font-weight: 800; color: #166534; }
        .receipt-detail { font-size: 10.5px; color: #166534; margin-top: 1px; }

        /* compact identification card (Dane badania) */
        .id-card { padding: 12px 18px; }
        .id-grid { display: flex; align-items: stretch; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        .id-item { flex: 1; min-width: 130px; padding: 2px 16px; border-left: 1px solid var(--line); }
        .id-item:first-child { padding-left: 0; border-left: none; }
        .id-k { display: block; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-muted); }
        .id-v { display: block; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); margin-top: 2px; word-break: break-word; }
        .id-pay { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
        .id-pay .chk { width: 22px; height: 22px; flex: 0 0 22px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
        .id-pay .chk svg { width: 13px; height: 13px; color: #fff; }
        .id-pay .pay-title { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; color: #166534; }
        .id-pay .pay-sub { font-size: 9px; color: #166534; margin-top: 1px; }

        /* ---------- Audiogram ---------- */
        .audiogram-card { text-align: center; padding: 12px 20px 14px; }
        .audiogram-svg { max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .audiogram-hint {
            font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.45;
            margin-top: 6px; max-width: 470px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;
        }

        /* frequency-range (max audible frequency) result + spectrum bar */
        .fr-head { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
        .fr-value { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary-dark); letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
        .fr-sub { font-size: 9.5px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.4px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-left: 8px; }

        .fr-bar-wrap { position: relative; margin: 32px 6px 6px; }
        .fr-bar-pill {
            position: absolute; top: -19px;
            background: var(--accent-dark); color: #fff; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 800;
            padding: 2px 7px; border-radius: 5px; white-space: nowrap;
        }
        .fr-bar {
            position: relative; height: 15px; border-radius: 8px;
            background: #EDF1F5; border: 1px solid var(--line); overflow: hidden;
        }
        .fr-bar-fill {
            position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #BFEACE 0%, var(--accent) 100%);
        }
        .fr-bar-needle {
            position: absolute; top: -2px; height: 19px; width: 0;
            border-left: 2px dashed #0F172A;
        }
        .fr-axis { position: relative; height: 12px; margin-top: 7px; }
        .fr-axis span {
            position: absolute; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-muted);
            transform: translateX(-50%); white-space: nowrap;
        }
        .fr-text { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-soft); margin-top: 16px; }

        /* ---------- Results table ---------- */
        .rtable { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
        .rtable th {
            font-size: 9.5px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.6px; text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            text-align: left;
            padding: 0 10px 10px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--line);
        }
        .rtable td {
            padding: 11px 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
            font-size: 12.5px;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }
        .rtable tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
        .rtable .freq { font-weight: 800; color: var(--text); white-space: nowrap; }
        .rtable .desc { color: var(--text-soft); }
        .rtable .db { font-weight: 800; color: var(--text); white-space: nowrap; }

        .bar-cell { width: 130px; }
        .bar-track { height: 7px; border-radius: 4px; background: #EEF1F4; overflow: hidden; }
        .bar-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 4px; }
        .level-normal .bar-fill,   .bar-fill.level-normal   { background: var(--normal); }
        .level-mild .bar-fill,     .bar-fill.level-mild     { background: #C99700; }
        .level-moderate .bar-fill, .bar-fill.level-moderate { background: var(--moderate); }
        .level-severe .bar-fill,   .bar-fill.level-severe   { background: var(--severe); }
        .level-profound .bar-fill, .bar-fill.level-profound { background: var(--profound); }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 10.5px;
            font-weight: 700;
            padding: 4px 11px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            color: #fff;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }
        .badge.level-normal   { background: var(--normal); }
        .badge.level-mild     { background: #8A6100; }
        .badge.level-moderate { background: var(--moderate); }
        .badge.level-severe   { background: var(--severe); }
        .badge.level-profound { background: var(--profound); }

        .legend {
            display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 14px;
            margin-top: 14px; padding-top: 12px;
            border-top: 1px dashed var(--line);
        }
        .legend-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-soft); font-weight: 600; }
        .legend-dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 3px; }

        /* ---------- Interpretation ---------- */
        .interp-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }
        .interp-block h4 {
            font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
        }
        .interp-block h4 svg { width: 15px; height: 15px; color: var(--primary); }
        .interp-block p { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-soft); }
        .steps { list-style: none; }
        .steps li {
            display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 8px;
            font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-soft);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .steps li .tick {
            flex: 0 0 17px; width: 17px; height: 17px; margin-top: 1px;
            border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent);
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
        }
        .steps li .tick svg { width: 11px; height: 11px; color: #fff; }

        /* ---------- Classification reference ---------- */
        .ref-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
        .ref-table th {
            font-size: 9.5px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--text-muted); text-align: left;
            padding: 0 10px 9px; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--line);
        }
        .ref-table td { padding: 9px 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); font-size: 11.5px; vertical-align: middle; }
        .ref-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
        .ref-table .range { font-weight: 800; color: var(--text); white-space: nowrap; }
        .ref-table .cls { white-space: nowrap; }
        .ref-table .meaning { color: var(--text-soft); }
        .ref-row-active td { background: #E0F7FA; }
        .ref-tag { display: inline-block; width: 9px; height: 9px; border-radius: 2px; margin-right: 6px; vertical-align: -1px; }

        /* ---------- Disclaimer + methodology ---------- */
        .disclaimer {
            margin-top: 22px;
            display: flex; gap: 12px;
            background: #FFFBEB;
            border: 1px solid #FDE68A;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 14px 16px;
            break-inside: avoid;
        }
        .disclaimer .ico { flex: 0 0 20px; width: 20px; height: 20px; color: #B45309; margin-top: 1px; }
        .disclaimer-title { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; color: #92400E; margin-bottom: 3px; }
        .disclaimer-text { font-size: 10.8px; color: #92400E; line-height: 1.55; }

        .methodology {
            margin-top: 16px;
            display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 16px;
            padding-top: 14px;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
        }
        .methodology .note { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-muted); max-width: 62%; }
        .methodology .sign { text-align: right; }
        .methodology .sign .name { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text); }
        .methodology .sign .role { font-size: 9.5px; color: var(--text-muted); }
        .methodology .sign .org  { font-size: 9.5px; color: var(--primary); font-weight: 700; margin-top: 2px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="sheet">

        <!-- ============ LETTERHEAD ============ -->
        <header class="letterhead">
            <div class="brand">
                <div class="logo">Sprawdź<span class="g">Słuch</span><span style="color:var(--primary)">.pl</span></div>
                <div class="tagline">Profesjonalny test słuchu online</div>
            </div>
            <div class="doc-meta">
                <div class="doc-kind">Raport z badania słuchu</div>
                <div class="doc-row">Nr raportu: <b>{{testId}}</b></div>
                <div class="doc-row">Data wystawienia: <b>{{reportDate}}</b></div>
            </div>
        </header>

        <!-- ============ EXAM DATA (identification) ============ -->
        <section class="section" style="margin-top:14px;">
            <div class="section-head">
                <span class="ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H7a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16l3.5-2 3.5 2 3.5-2L19 21z"/><line x1="9" y1="7" x2="15" y2="7"/><line x1="9" y1="11" x2="15" y2="11"/></svg></span>
                <h2 class="section-title">Dane badania</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="card id-card">
                <div class="id-grid">
                    <div class="id-item">
                        <span class="id-k">Pacjent (e-mail)</span>
                        <span class="id-v">{{userEmail}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="id-item">
                        <span class="id-k">Identyfikator badania</span>
                        <span class="id-v">{{testId}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="id-item">
                        <span class="id-k">Data badania</span>
                        <span class="id-v">{{testDate}}</span>
                    </div>
                    {{#if payment}}
                    <div class="id-item id-pay">
                        <span class="chk"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span>
                        <span>
                            <span class="pay-title">Opłacono</span>
                            <span class="pay-sub">{{payment.method}} · {{payment.paymentId}}</span>
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ============ RESULT SUMMARY (HERO) ============ -->
        <section class="summary {{summary.levelClass}}">
            <div class="summary-label">Wynik badania</div>
            <div class="summary-status">{{summary.status}}</div>
            <p class="summary-meaning">{{summary.meaning}}</p>

            <div class="meter-wrap">
                <div class="meter-scalelabels">
                    <span>0 dB · norma</span>
                    <span>40</span>
                    <span>70</span>
                    <span>100 dB · głęboki</span>
                </div>
                <div class="meter">
                    <div class="meter-marker" style="left: {{summary.meterPercent}}%;"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="meter-caption">Znacznik wskazuje Twój średni próg słyszenia (PTA). Im bliżej lewej strony skali, tym lepszy słuch.</div>
            </div>

            <div class="stats">
                <div class="stat">
                    <div class="k">Średni próg słyszenia (PTA)</div>
                    <div class="v">{{summary.averageLevel}} dB</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat">
                    <div class="k">Maks. słyszalna częstotliwość</div>
                    <div class="v">{{maxAudibleFrequency}}</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ============ AUDIOGRAM ============ -->
        <section class="section">
            <div class="section-head">
                <span class="ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 12h3l3-7 4 14 3-7h5"/></svg></span>
                <h2 class="section-title">Audiogram</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="card audiogram-card">
                {{#if audiogram}}
                    <div class="audiogram-svg">{{{audiogram}}}</div>
                    <p class="audiogram-hint">Niebieska krzywa to Twój próg słyszenia dla każdej częstotliwości — im niżej leży punkt, tym słabsza słyszalność danego tonu. Zielona linia wyznacza najwyższą słyszalną przez Ciebie częstotliwość. Tło oznacza strefy ubytku słuchu.</p>
                {{else}}
                    <p class="audiogram-hint">Brak danych do wygenerowania wykresu. Szczegółowe wyniki znajdują się w tabeli poniżej.</p>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ============ FREQUENCY RANGE (max audible frequency) ============ -->
        {{#if frequencyRange}}
        <section class="section">
            <div class="section-head">
                <span class="ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M2 10v3"/><path d="M6 6v11"/><path d="M10 3v18"/><path d="M14 8v7"/><path d="M18 5v13"/><path d="M22 10v3"/></svg></span>
                <h2 class="section-title">Zakres słyszanych częstotliwości</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="fr-head">
                    <div><span class="fr-value">{{frequencyRange.valueLabel}}</span><span class="fr-sub">maks. słyszalna częstotliwość</span></div>
                    <span class="badge {{frequencyRange.levelClass}}">{{frequencyRange.rating}}</span>
                </div>

                <div class="fr-bar-wrap">
                    <div class="fr-bar-pill" style="left: {{frequencyRange.barPercent}}%; transform: translateX({{frequencyRange.pillShift}});">Twój zakres: {{frequencyRange.valueLabel}}</div>
                    <div class="fr-bar">
                        <div class="fr-bar-fill" style="width: {{frequencyRange.barPercent}}%;"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="fr-bar-needle" style="left: {{frequencyRange.barPercent}}%;"></div>
                    <div class="fr-axis">
                        <span style="left:0%; transform:translateX(0);">3 kHz</span>
                        <span style="left:26.9%;">5</span>
                        <span style="left:51.7%;">8</span>
                        <span style="left:73.1%;">12</span>
                        <span style="left:100%; transform:translateX(-100%);">20 kHz</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p class="fr-text">{{frequencyRange.text}} Zielony pasek pokazuje zakres słyszanych przez Ciebie częstotliwości na tle pełnego pasma słuchu człowieka (do 20 kHz).</p>
            </div>
        </section>
        {{/if}}

        <!-- ============ DETAILED RESULTS ============ -->
        <section class="section">
            <div class="section-head">
                <span class="ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="8" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="21" y2="12"/><line x1="8" y1="18" x2="21" y2="18"/><line x1="3" y1="6" x2="3.01" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="12" x2="3.01" y2="12"/><line x1="3" y1="18" x2="3.01" y2="18"/></svg></span>
                <h2 class="section-title">Szczegółowe wyniki</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <table class="rtable">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th style="width:78px;">Częstotl.</th>
                            <th>Zakres tonów</th>
                            <th style="width:62px;">Próg</th>
                            <th class="bar-cell">Poziom</th>
                            <th style="width:130px;">Ocena</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        {{#each hearingResults}}
                        <tr>
                            <td class="freq">{{frequencyLabel}}</td>
                            <td class="desc">{{description}}</td>
                            <td class="db">{{level}} dB</td>
                            <td class="bar-cell">
                                <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill {{levelClass}}" style="width: {{barWidth}}%;"></div></div>
                            </td>
                            <td><span class="badge {{levelClass}}">{{interpretation}}</span></td>
                        </tr>
                        {{/each}}
                    </tbody>
                </table>

                <div class="legend">
                    <div class="legend-item"><span class="legend-dot" style="background:var(--normal)"></span>Norma (0–20 dB)</div>
                    <div class="legend-item"><span class="legend-dot" style="background:#C99700"></span>Lekki (21–40 dB)</div>
                    <div class="legend-item"><span class="legend-dot" style="background:var(--moderate)"></span>Umiarkowany (41–70 dB)</div>
                    <div class="legend-item"><span class="legend-dot" style="background:var(--severe)"></span>Znaczny (71–90 dB)</div>
                    <div class="legend-item"><span class="legend-dot" style="background:var(--profound)"></span>Głęboki (&gt;90 dB)</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ============ INTERPRETATION + NEXT STEPS ============ -->
        <section class="section">
            <div class="section-head">
                <span class="ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12.01" y2="8"/></svg></span>
                <h2 class="section-title">Interpretacja i zalecenia</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="interp-grid">
                    <div class="interp-block">
                        <h4><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg>Co oznacza Twój wynik</h4>
                        <p>{{summary.meaning}}</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="interp-block">
                        <h4><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"/><path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"/></svg>Zalecane kroki</h4>
                        <ul class="steps">
                            {{#each summary.nextSteps}}
                            <li><span class="tick"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span><span>{{this}}</span></li>
                            {{/each}}
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ============ CLASSIFICATION REFERENCE ============ -->
        <section class="section">
            <div class="section-head">
                <span class="ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg></span>
                <h2 class="section-title">Jak czytać wynik — klasyfikacja ubytku słuchu</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <table class="ref-table">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th style="width:110px;">Próg (dB)</th>
                            <th style="width:150px;">Klasyfikacja</th>
                            <th>Co to oznacza w praktyce</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr class="{{#if (eq summary.levelClass 'level-normal')}}ref-row-active{{/if}}">
                            <td class="range">0–20</td>
                            <td class="cls"><span class="ref-tag" style="background:var(--normal)"></span>Norma</td>
                            <td class="meaning">Słuch prawidłowy — bez trudności w codziennym słyszeniu.</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr class="{{#if (eq summary.levelClass 'level-mild')}}ref-row-active{{/if}}">
                            <td class="range">21–40</td>
                            <td class="cls"><span class="ref-tag" style="background:#C99700"></span>Lekki ubytek</td>
                            <td class="meaning">Możliwe trudności z cichą mową oraz rozmową w hałasie.</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr class="{{#if (eq summary.levelClass 'level-moderate')}}ref-row-active{{/if}}">
                            <td class="range">41–70</td>
                            <td class="cls"><span class="ref-tag" style="background:var(--moderate)"></span>Umiarkowany</td>
                            <td class="meaning">Trudności w typowej rozmowie; często wskazana diagnostyka.</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr class="{{#if (eq summary.levelClass 'level-severe')}}ref-row-active{{/if}}">
                            <td class="range">71–90</td>
                            <td class="cls"><span class="ref-tag" style="background:var(--severe)"></span>Znaczny</td>
                            <td class="meaning">Rozumienie mowy mocno ograniczone bez aparatu słuchowego.</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr class="{{#if (eq summary.levelClass 'level-profound')}}ref-row-active{{/if}}">
                            <td class="range">&gt; 90</td>
                            <td class="cls"><span class="ref-tag" style="background:var(--profound)"></span>Głęboki</td>
                            <td class="meaning">Mowa praktycznie niesłyszalna bez wsparcia aparatem/implantem.</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ============ FREQUENCY GUIDE ============ -->
        <section class="section">
            <div class="section-head">
                <span class="ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 18v-6a9 9 0 0 1 18 0v6"/><path d="M21 19a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-1a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-3a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h3z"/><path d="M3 19a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h1a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-3a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H3z"/></svg></span>
                <h2 class="section-title">Co oznaczają badane częstotliwości</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <table class="ref-table">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th style="width:150px;">Zakres</th>
                            <th style="width:210px;">Przykładowe dźwięki</th>
                            <th>Dlaczego jest ważny</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="range">Niskie<br><span style="font-weight:600;color:var(--text-muted);font-size:10px;">250–500 Hz</span></td>
                            <td class="meaning">Samogłoski, niski męski głos, buczenie urządzeń.</td>
                            <td class="meaning">Odpowiadają za odczuwaną głośność i „pełnię” mowy.</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="range">Średnie<br><span style="font-weight:600;color:var(--text-muted);font-size:10px;">1–2 kHz</span></td>
                            <td class="meaning">Większość mowy, rozmowa telefoniczna.</td>
                            <td class="meaning">Kluczowe dla rozumienia, o czym mówi rozmówca.</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="range">Wysokie<br><span style="font-weight:600;color:var(--text-muted);font-size:10px;">4–8 kHz</span></td>
                            <td class="meaning">Spółgłoski (s, f, t), ptaki, dzwonek, „sz”.</td>
                            <td class="meaning">Decydują o wyrazistości mowy — tu ubytek pojawia się najczęściej.</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ============ DISCLAIMER ============ -->
        <div class="disclaimer">
            <svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M10.29 3.86 1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg>
            <div>
                <div class="disclaimer-title">Ważne — charakter orientacyjny</div>
                <div class="disclaimer-text">Niniejszy raport jest wynikiem przesiewowego testu słuchu wykonanego online i ma charakter orientacyjny. Nie stanowi diagnozy medycznej i nie zastępuje badania audiologicznego w gabinecie. W razie wątpliwości lub niepokojących wyników skonsultuj się z lekarzem laryngologiem albo audiologiem.</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ============ METHODOLOGY / SIGNATURE ============ -->
        <div class="methodology">
            <div class="note">Metodologia oparta na uznanych standardach audiometrii tonalnej (próg słyszenia dla częstotliwości 250–8000 Hz) oraz na pomiarze maksymalnej słyszalnej częstotliwości. Wynik ma charakter przesiewowy i wygenerowano go automatycznie na podstawie odpowiedzi udzielonych podczas testu.</div>
            <div class="sign">
                <div class="name">Zespół SprawdźSłuch</div>
                <div class="role">Nadzór merytoryczny: specjalista audiolog</div>
                <div class="org">www.sprawdzsluch.pl · kontakt@sprawdzsluch.pl</div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</body>
</html>
